node.text:
Crispy outside, tender inside, that’s I like about @cpfoodssg Japanese Chicken Crispy & Chicken Dippers. 😋 Both are amongst our family’s favourite CP products. What’s your favourite CP items? .
.
With CP Foods’s vast array of ready-to-eat offerings, you and your family members can savour the classic and eclectic cuisines of Japan, Italy, Thailand and Mexico without even having to step out of the house. Enjoy 15% off sitewide on their full range of products and free home delivery with min. purchase of $89.00
